		{"id":"a320d5a022ae7e80","x":-1054,"y":-583,"width":346,"height":530,"color":"6","type":"text","text":"Multi region, Active  Active\n\n2 regions, has mutliple AZs , two regions has an active (read & write) instances, trafiic is distributed least latency\n\n![[Pasted image 20260403221358.png]]"},
		{"id":"5a27cab005d40825","x":-1489,"y":-583,"width":389,"height":530,"color":"6","type":"text","text":"Multi region, Active Passive\n\n2 regions, has one or mutliple AZs , one region has an active (read & write) instance and a passive instance (can only read)\n\nTraffic flows primarilly from the active \n\n![[Pasted image 20260403221422.png]]"},
		{"id":"61edce80c3b24725","x":-1028,"y":-1033,"width":320,"height":382,"color":"6","type":"text","text":"Single region, Multi AZ\n\nApplication spans at least two AZs witihn one region\n\n![[Pasted image 20260403221524.png]]"},
